<Algorithm code="           1. Let _O_ be _taRecord_.[[Object]].           1. Let _bufferByteLength_ be _taRecord_.[[CachedBufferByteLength]].           1. Assert: IsDetachedBuffer(_O_.[[ViewedArrayBuffer]]) is *true* if and only if _bufferByteLength_ is ~detached~.           1. If _bufferByteLength_ is ~detached~, return *true*.           1. Let _byteOffsetStart_ be _O_.[[ByteOffset]].           1. If _O_.[[ArrayLength]] is ~auto~, then             1. Let _byteOffsetEnd_ be _bufferByteLength_.           1. Else,             1. Let _elementSize_ be TypedArrayElementSize(_O_).             1. Let _byteOffsetEnd_ be _byteOffsetStart_ + _O_.[[ArrayLength]] × _elementSize_.           1. If _byteOffsetStart_ &gt; _bufferByteLength_ or _byteOffsetEnd_ &gt; _bufferByteLength_, return *true*.           1. NOTE: 0-length TypedArrays are not considered out-of-bounds.           1. Return *false*.         ">
